Package me.taylorkelly.mywarp.warp

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Warp
    Represents a Warp.
    WarpManager
    Manages Warps and provides utility methods to get certain informations based on the Warps managed by it.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractWarpManager
    An abstract WarpManager implementation that implements 'matching' methods that do not depend on the implementation.
    EventfullWarp
    Forwards method calls to an existing Warp and posts WarpEvents to an EventWarpManager.
    EventWarpManager
    Provides an event-framework for the Warps managed by it.
    ForwardingWarp
    A Warp which forwards all its method calls to another Warp.
    SimpleWarp
    The simple implementation of a Warp.
    Warp.PopularityComparator
    A custom comparator that orders Warps by there popularity: popular Warps come first, unpopular last.
    WarpBuilder
    A Builder for warps.
    WarpSignManager
    Manages warp signs.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Warp.Type
    The type of a Warp.
